    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Asuan - Abu Simbel</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">‚Üê</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Asuan - Abu Simbel</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Excursie de 2 zile cu autobuzul. In prima zi programul este identic ca cel de mai sus in Asuan, dupamiaza tarziu vei fi cazat intr-un hotel in Asuan.
        Ziua urmatoare la ora 04:00 dupa micul dejun, transferul cu un convoi militar catre Abu Simbel (aproximativ la 300km departare).
        -vizita la  cele 2  mari si simbolice monuente ale Egiptului - templele Ramses II, sunt facute sa arate puterea si sa impresioneze strainii care ajung din sudul Egiptului.
        Templele au fost descoperite in 1813 de Jacoba Burckhardta, calatorul din Switzerland. Pranzul este inclus, bauturile sunt conta cost. In jurul orei 21:00 ajungi la hotel.
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        marti si miercuri
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Two days excursion by bus. The first day visit program is identical as above in Asuan, late afternoon You will 
        check-in to hotel in Asuan. Next day early at 04:00 AM after breakfast, the transfer with military convoy to Abu 
        Simbel (ab.300km away)- visit in two biggest and very symbolic monuments of Egypt- Ramses II temples, that 
        were meant to show the power and to impress foreigners arriving from south to Egypt. Temples were 
        discovered in 1813 by Jacoba Burckhardta, the traveller from Switzerland. Lunch included, drinks extra charge. 
        Around 21:00 arriving to the hotel.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Tuesday and Wednesday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>